          "name": "preparationHandler",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The block invoked by "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uicloudsharingcontroller"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " when it is time for your application to save a newly created "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/cloudkit/ckshare"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " record."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Use the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uicloudsharingcontroller/1649607-initwithpreparationhandler"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " initializer method to create a new "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uicloudsharingcontroller"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " instance when the user who owns a "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/cloudkit/ckrecord"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " wants to share the record with other people. To determine if the record is shared, check its "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/cloudkit/ckrecord/1640378-share"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property. If the property value is "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "nil"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", the record is not shared, and this method is the one to use."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "aside",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "You must initialize the controller with the correct initializer method. Do not use "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": false,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uicloudsharingcontroller/1649607-initwithpreparationhandler"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " if the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/cloudkit/ckrecord"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " is already shared. Likewise, do not use "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uicloudsharingcontroller/1649597-initwithshare"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " if the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/cloudkit/ckrecord"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " is not shared. Using the wrong initializer leads to errors when saving the record."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "style": "important"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "preparationHandler:"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " provided to the initializer method is responsible for saving the new "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/cloudkit/ckshare"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " record. The handler has two parameters:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "unorderedList",
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "A reference to the "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uicloudsharingcontroller"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " instance that called the preparation handler"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "A reference to a completion block"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "After you save the new "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/cloudkit/ckshare"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " record and its root record (the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/cloudkit/ckrecord"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " representing the data to share) in the preparation handler, you call the completion block. Calling the completion block tells the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uicloudsharingcontroller"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " instance to continue with the invitation workflow."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For more information and sample code, see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uicloudsharingcontroller#2647064"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
